OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778782268
OL,3,CSt Pauls Carnival scaled back this
OL,4,Cyear amid cost and security concerns
OL,6,FThe organisers of St Pauls Carnival
OL,7,Fhave confirmed that a full-scale event
OL,8,Fwill not take place this year.
OL,10,FFollowing ongoing discussions with
OL,11,Fpartners including Bristol City
OL,12,FCouncil and Avon and Somerset Police,
OL,13,FSt Pauls Carnival CIC Board say that
OL,14,Fit is not possible to "safely and
OL,15,Fsustainably" deliver the carnival at
OL,16,Fthe scale and size the community have
OL,17,Fcome to expect.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
