CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778782268
OL,3,CSt Pauls Carnival scaled back this
OL,4,Cyear amid cost and security concerns
OL,6,FThe Bristol carnival began in 1968 and
OL,7,Fcelebrates African Caribbean culture
OL,8,Fand creativity, with live music,
OL,9,Fprocessions, and dancing throughout
OL,10,Fthe streets of St Pauls.
OL,12,FOrganisers added that they have been
OL,13,Fconsidering alternative delivery
OL,14,Fmodels, including a revised schedule,
OL,15,Fbut it's become clear the popular
OL,16,Fevent can't be delivered in its
OL,17,Ftraditional form this year "without
OL,18,Fexposing the organisation to an
OL,19,Funacceptable level of operational and
OL,20,Ffinancial risk".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778782268
OL,3,CSt Pauls Carnival scaled back this
OL,4,Cyear amid cost and security concerns
OL,6,FWhile the full-scale event won't
OL,7,Fhappen in 2026, organisers say they're
OL,8,Fcommitted to delivering a schedule of
OL,9,Fcommunity event throughout the year,
OL,10,Fincluding costume-making, cultural
OL,11,Feducation in schools, and a family-
OL,12,Foriented carnival celebration later
OL,13,Fthis summer.
OL,15,FOrganisers are also working on a
OL,16,Ftraining and development programme to
OL,17,Finvolve local people in the
OL,18,Forganisation in the future delivery of
OL,19,Fthe vibrant carnival.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
