PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778782268
OL,3,CSt Pauls Carnival scaled back this
OL,4,Cyear amid cost and security concerns
OL,6,FA statement from the SPC Board reads:
OL,7,F"This has been an incredibly difficult
OL,8,Fdecision and one that we know will be
OL,9,Fdisappointing for the community and
OL,10,Fthe wider public. St Pauls Carnival is
OL,11,Fa unique and deeply valued celebration
OL,12,Fof African Caribbean culture, heritage
OL,13,Fand community, and we fully recognise
OL,14,Fthe disappointment many people will
OL,15,Ffeel.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778782268
OL,3,CSt Pauls Carnival scaled back this
OL,4,Cyear amid cost and security concerns
OL,6,F"Over the past year, we have worked
OL,7,Fclosely with the community, our
OL,8,Fpartners and operational teams to
OL,9,Fexplore how the full Carnival could
OL,10,Freturn in a way that reflects both the
OL,11,Fcultural significance of the event and
OL,12,Fthe operational realities involved in
OL,13,Fdelivering a free-to-attend public
OL,14,Fstreet event which attracts 150,000
OL,15,Fpeople.
OL,17,F"Despite considerable work to reduce
OL,18,Fcosts and reshape the model, as a
OL,19,Fboard we have ultimately reached the
OL,20,Fconclusion that delivering a full-
OL,21,Fscale Carnival in 2026 is not viable.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778782268
OL,3,CSt Pauls Carnival scaled back this
OL,4,Cyear amid cost and security concerns
OL,6,F"Our responsibility must always be to
OL,7,Fprotect the safety of the public,
OL,8,Fvolunteers, artists, traders, staff
OL,9,Fand everyone involved in bringing
OL,10,FCarnival to life.
OL,12,F"Delivering an event which has grown
OL,13,Fto this scale in recent years requires
OL,14,Fsubstantial infrastructure, safety
OL,15,Fmanagement, staffing and financial
OL,16,Fresources.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778782268
OL,3,CSt Pauls Carnival scaled back this
OL,4,Cyear amid cost and security concerns
OL,6,F"Like many cultural and live events
OL,7,Forganisations across the UK, we face
OL,8,Fincreasing financial pressure on
OL,9,Finfrastructure, staffing, safety,
OL,10,Fsecurity, compliance and delivery
OL,11,Fcosts.
OL,13,F"Despite extensive fundraising
OL,14,Factivity and ongoing partner support,
OL,15,Fthe gap between available resources
OL,16,Fand the costs required to deliver
OL,17,FCarnival safely and responsibly
OL,18,Fremained too significant for 2026.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1778782268
OL,3,CSt Pauls Carnival scaled back this
OL,4,Cyear amid cost and security concerns
OL,6,F"While a full-scale Carnival will not
OL,7,Ftake place this summer, our work to
OL,8,Fcelebrate, protect and invest in
OL,9,FCarnival's cultural legacy absolutely
OL,10,Fcontinues. This is not the end of
OL,11,FCarnival. It is a necessary reset to
OL,12,Fhelp ensure its long-term future."
OL,14,FLast year, the carnival took place in
OL,15,Fa scaled-back version, following a
OL,16,Fdecision by organisers to hold the
OL,17,Fparade every other year due to
OL,18,Fspiralling costs.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
